  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ali Sabri and Vijayadasa go to Geneva",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The 51st session of the Human Rights Council (HRC) is scheduled to be held in Geneva from 12 September - 07 October 2022.",
        "Minister of Foreign Affairs Ali Sabri, who will lead the Sri Lankan delegation, will make a statement to the Council at the interactive dialogue on Sri Lanka to be held on Monday, September 12, 2022.",
        "Minister of Justice, Prison Affairs and Constitutional Reform Dr. Vijayadasa Rajapaksa will also be included in this delegation."
      ],
